# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../files.rst:152
msgid ""
"When optimization is in progress, the submenu changes to a single :guilabel:"
"`Cancel` action for the selected file(s). Optimized preview files are used "
"only for editing and preview playback. Your final export still uses the "
"original source files."
msgstr ""
